name: createGeneralLedgerEntry

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'General Ledger Entry' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {General Ledger,General Ledger Entries}

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[@class = 'sidebar-menu-container'] (tried for 10 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

testSteps.description: Then the 'G/L Header Information' page should show up
When I set the currency to 'USD'
When I set the description to 'TEST1'
When I click 'Continue' button
Then the 'G/L Distribution' page should show up
When I set the Account Number to '911000'
When I set the Line Description to 'TEST1'
When I set the Amount to '1000'
When I set the Employee to 'Taramarcaz'
When I set the General Obj to 'AFGHAIG'
When i click show next button
When I set the 'Project ID' to 'DEFAULT PROJECT'
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'DEFAULT PROJECT1'
Then the project ID field should be empty
When I set the 'Line Ref' to 'DEFAULT PROJECT1'
When I set the 'Project ID' to 'DEFAULT PROJECT'
Then the line ref field should be empty
When I click the 'Select Cash' Button
Then the 'Select CASH Account' modal should show up
When I select first checkbox from 'Select Cash' modal
When I click 'Submit' button
When I click 'Proceed' button
Then the 'General Ledger Entry successfully created' modal should show up

title: Create general ledger entry
